$columns.name: registrationNotes

onChange.script:
#Script to determine if we can proceed to the next page of registration
	fields = currentValue.value
	proceed = True
	needed = ''
	for field in fields:
		if fields[field].value == False: 
			proceed = False
			if needed == '':
				needed = field
	self.params.proceed = proceed
	self.params.neededToProceed = needed

value = self.custom.info
	guestCount = value.getValueAt(0,'capacity')
	AdditionalNights = len(self.params.schedule)
	NewBedsProjected = AdditionalNights * guestCount
	self.getChild("root").getChild("History Small_Double_Flex").props.params.RightValue = NewBedsProjected
